title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show  DEC-06-2013 FRI
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show  DEC-06-2013 FRI






Friday, December 06, 2013
Pope Francis On Capitalism And Movie Review
 
 

 - 9AM hour

Mike discusses Pope Francis' comments on capitalism




 - 10AM hour

Sarah Janssen, Senior Editor of "The World Almanac,"
           joins Mike to tell us about this year's Almanac
              and Mike talks about Detroit filing for bankruptcy.

 - 11AM hour

Movie Review: Mike and Christian Toto review the latest installment of the Hunger Games.

            Be sure to follow Christian on his blog: http://daddylibrium.com/
